{"tid":1507834,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【一人一實體信炸爆教育局】","createTime":"2019-08-26T10:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:18:17.000Z","uid":38075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4102a2363d4519b571a1616b6f12f210fbd213ed","tid":1507834,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"代一眾熱心教師出post<br />\n<br />\n早前教育局發出開學指引，建議老師在討論社會發生的事時容許自己說「不知道」或「自己也不理解」，有違教師的專業操守。 <br />\n<br />\n我們已準備好回應教育局的信，讓大家Print出來寄給局長，建議各位可以: <br />\n <br />\n1. Download 我們提供的信件Template <br />\n  或 <br />\n在Template後手寫字句，補充自己的意見 <br />\n  或 <br />\n親手撰寫另一封回應信 <br />\n <br />\n2.把信件郵寄至以下地址: <br />\n香港灣仔皇后大道東213號胡忠大廈15樓  教育局局長  楊潤雄先生 <br />\n <br />\n3.寄之前可拍照打卡，以作留念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打卡照請 Inbox 我地係香港老師fb 或 TG dm俾 @sillybb1234 讓我們集集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下為信件template:<br />\n<br />\n1. 圖片版（可直接以白紙列印）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/395CzZ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F395CzZ1.jpg&h=8eb581d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74EG1E2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74EG1E2.jpg&h=df0aead7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ED1KeZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FED1KeZ4.jpg&h=46406be2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/shDHL6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FshDHL6N.jpg&h=2d14d1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. PDF版<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/11BSeM6cYhhRdpkyGbaScgQqUs4Pml0jU/view?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F11BSeM6cYh